text:
Kaho worked hard to win these snacks...
I wonder if it's okay to have so many.

Of course it is! Winning the sports festival
was thanks to everyone!

Oh, it is! How cute.
Does it come with a toy?
Oh, it's an unexpected exhibition match!?

Natsuha-san!
Please pass it to me!!

Wait, hold on!
Where's the goal!? What about the teams!?
